  ---and   ah.AgentType in (2, 46, 47, 49)	
  and   a.Agt_Type in (2, 46, 47, 49)																--  MF 14/03/2024 (AgentType Column not available in S_Agents) 
  and   a.CompetentStatus in (1,2)																	--- MF 14/03/2024 Tech debt replacement 
---  and   ah.Active = 1																			--- MF 14/03/2024 Tech debt: Column not available in S_Agents


